{"title":"用.cursorrules，让AI自动写出高级 UI","slug":"qvdptvgdmrp37pvy","summary":"很多做 Vibe Coding 的朋友问我：“为什么我的 AI 写出来的界面总是那种‘默认Bootstrap风’，或者配色脏脏的？” 🤯 因为你没有给 AI 植入“审美芯片”。 作为产品设计师，我受不了每次都要重复通过 Prompt 告诉 AI “要留白、要圆角、不要纯黑”。所","category":"Vibe Coding技巧","tags":["PART1️⃣ AI设计工作流&Vibe Coding","Vibe Coding技巧"],"featured":false,"order":36,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-01-19","wordCount":431,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/qvdptvgdmrp37pvy","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u1a715a18\" id=\"u1a715a18\"><span data-lake-id=\"u78c57a18\" id=\"u78c57a18\">很多做 Vibe Coding 的朋友问我：“为什么我的 AI 写出来的界面总是那种‘默认Bootstrap风’，或者配色脏脏的？” </span><span data-lake-id=\"u030a99b5\" id=\"u030a99b5\">🤯</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4f496d64\" id=\"u4f496d64\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf2923def\" id=\"uf2923def\">因为你没有给 AI 植入“审美芯片”。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufba819e4\" id=\"ufba819e4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2ba085f5\" id=\"u2ba085f5\">作为产品设计师，我受不了每次都要重复通过 Prompt 告诉 AI “要留白、要圆角、不要纯黑”。所以我把这些设计原则写进了项目的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u91f24c90\" id=\"u91f24c90\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6ec45339\" id=\"u6ec45339\">.cursorrules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufc776c48\" id=\"ufc776c48\"> 文件里。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7f4cfa48\" id=\"u7f4cfa48\"><span data-lake-id=\"u384bcd7c\" id=\"u384bcd7c\">📂</span><span data-lake-id=\"uff872a03\" id=\"uff872a03\"> </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u913f6902\" id=\"u913f6902\">什么是 .cursorrules？</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8322dc69\" id=\"u8322dc69\"> 在你的项目根目录下创建一个名为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ubb62c59d\" id=\"ubb62c59d\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf7b98378\" id=\"uf7b98378\">.cursorrules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udf1c9ea8\" id=\"udf1c9ea8\"> 的文件，Cursor 会自动读取这里的指令，作为它写代码的“出厂设置”。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2260f6ef\" id=\"u2260f6ef\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1d498fa8\" id=\"u1d498fa8\">👇</span><span data-lake-id=\"u9e7eca68\" id=\"u9e7eca68\"> </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua22e9a65\" id=\"ua22e9a65\">直接复制下面这段配置（UI 篇）：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ueb45dbb4\" id=\"ueb45dbb4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf0cefaaa\" id=\"uf0cefaaa\">Markdown</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22plain%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22You%20are%20an%20expert%20UI%2FUX%20designer%20and%20frontend%20developer.%5CnAlways%20prioritizing%20%5C%22Clean%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22Minimalist%5C%22%2C%20and%20%5C%22Modern%5C%22%20aesthetics.%5Cn%5Cn%23%20UI%20Design%20Principles%5Cn1.%20%20**Whitespace%20is%20King%3A**%20Always%20use%20ample%20padding%20(p-6%2C%20p-8)%20and%20gap%20(gap-4%2C%20gap-6).%20Avoid%20dense%20layouts.%20Content%20should%20breathe.%5Cn2.%20%20**Color%20Palette%3A**%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20NEVER%20use%20pure%20black%20(%23000).%20Use%20Zinc%2FSlate-950%20for%20dark%20text.%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Use%20Zinc%2FSlate-500%20for%20secondary%20text.%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Backgrounds%20should%20be%20subtle%20off-white%20or%20very%20light%20gray%20(bg-zinc-50%2F10)%20to%20create%20depth.%5Cn3.%20%20**Visual%20Hierarchy%3A**%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Headings%20(H1%2C%20H2)%20must%20be%20bold%20and%20tracking-tight.%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Use%20muted%20colors%20for%20borders%20(border-zinc-200).%5Cn4.%20%20**Micro-Interactions%3A**%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Buttons%20and%20cards%20must%20have%20subtle%20hover%20states.%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Use%20%60transition-all%20duration-300%20ease-in-out%60%20for%20smooth%20effects.%5Cn5.%20%20**Components%3A**%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Prefer%20Shadcn%20UI%20%2F%20Radix%20UI%20components.%5Cn%20%20%20%20-%20%20%20Use%20rounded-xl%20or%20rounded-2xl%20for%20cards%20to%20feel%20modern.%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B4%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22contain%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GfbjE%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22contain%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u091bf01e\" id=\"u091bf01e\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc524890f\" id=\"uc524890f\">为什么这套配置好用？</span></strong></p><ol list=\"ucdd89f2c\"><li fid=\"u10af8d19\" data-lake-id=\"u16f7272b\" id=\"u16f7272b\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc01bd456\" id=\"uc01bd456\">强制留白：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uedd337eb\" id=\"uedd337eb\"> 解决了“界面太挤”的通病。</span></li><li fid=\"u10af8d19\" data-lake-id=\"u9ce75f57\" id=\"u9ce75f57\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue86d6268\" id=\"ue86d6268\">消灭纯黑：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8c5d8640\" id=\"u8c5d8640\"> 用深灰色代替纯黑，质感立马提升 10 倍。</span></li><li fid=\"u10af8d19\" data-lake-id=\"ua0c42699\" id=\"ua0c42699\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uadfbfd1c\" id=\"uadfbfd1c\">默认圆角：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue7750951\" id=\"ue7750951\"> 告别直角的生硬感，更符合现代 SaaS 的趋势。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u811fa336\" id=\"u811fa336\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58b6d772\" id=\"u58b6d772\">把这段话喂给你的 Cursor，你会发现它写出来的 Demo 就像经过设计师调优了一样。</span><span data-lake-id=\"uab88fa35\" id=\"uab88fa35\">✨</span></p>"}
